ext_onboarding_description_consent_warn_.message:
The company managing this device, or your company administrator has selected to protect this computer with security products by WithSecure. The configuration enforces protecting users of the computer from harmful web sites. To provide the core functionality of the Browsing Protection by WithSecure - prevent malicious websites from causing you harm, we need your consent to collect and process the data. You will not be able to use the extension otherwise.
By you allowing Browsing Protection by WithSecure, you accept that the addresses of websites you visit are transferred to the WithSecure security products to check its rating and category. The addresses (URLs) are made non-identifiable and handled by our automated WithSecure Security Cloud in accordance with our $PRIVACY_POLICY$.
Consent needed to protect your browsing
